<Layouts.app flash={@flash}>
  <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-12 mt-5 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <.custom_nav active="chelekom-docs-banner" />
    <div class="lg:col-span-10">
      <.custom_info
        title="Banner"
        description="Customizable, dismissible banners for Phoenix LiveView with flexible positioning and smooth animation transitions to enhance user interaction."
        mix="mix mishka.ui.gen.component banner"
        github="https://github.com/mishka-group/mishka_chelekom/blob/master/priv/components/banner.eex"
        tags={["Component", "Stateless", "JS-module"]}
      />
      <.custom_tab id="chelekom-banner-tab">
        <:documentation_panel>
          <.heading2 class="mb-5" id="overview">
            <.link patch={~p"/chelekom/docs/banner/#overview"}>
              Overview of the Phoenix and LiveView Banner Component
            </.link>
          </.heading2>

          <.cp>
            The
            <strong>
              Mishka Chelekom Banner
            </strong>
            module provides versatile banners with a variety of styles and colors. It offers an effective way to display announcements, notifications, or important information. Support components like <strong>
    Dismissable Banners
  </strong>,
            which allow users to hide banners with a smooth transition, enhancing user control and interactivity.
          </.cp>

          <.cp margin="mt-5">
            The Mishka Chelekom <strong>Banner component</strong>
            integrates seamlessly with <strong>Phoenix</strong>
            LiveView applications, offering customizable positioning and sizes to fit any design. With this <strong><.link
                title="Phoenix LiveView component"
                class="transition-colors hover:text-[#448D96]"
                navigate={~p"/chelekom"}
              >
  Phoenix LiveView component
  </.link></strong>,
            users can display banners for promotions, warnings, or announcements, with real-time updates.
          </.cp>

          <.heading2 margin="my-5" id="base-banner">
            <.link patch={~p"/chelekom/docs/banner/#base-banner"}>
              Base Variant
            </.link>
          </.heading2>

          <.custom_code_wrapper code_class="text-sm" code={@code_17}>
            <div class="mb-6 flex justify-center items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
              <.button
                size="small"
                phx-click="banner_position"
                phx-value-pos="banner-example-120"
                variant="outline"
                color="natural"
              >
                Show base
              </.button>
            </div>

            <.banner
              :if={@banner_pos == "banner-example-120"}
              id="banner_natural_doc_120"
              dismiss_size="extra_large"
            >
              Base color and variant banner component
            </.banner>
          </.custom_code_wrapper>

          <.heading2 margin="my-5" id="default-variant-banner">
            <.link patch={~p"/chelekom/docs/banner/#default-variant-banner"}>
              Default Variant
            </.link>
          </.heading2>

          <.cp>
            The default style of the Mishka Chelekom banner applies a solid background and border that change based on user interaction, making it perfect for delivering important notifications. With just a single setting, you can select from a range of color options, ensuring easy customization to match various design styles.
          </.cp>

          <.custom_code_wrapper code_class="text-sm" code={@code_1}>
            <div class="mb-6 flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
              <.button
                size="small"
                phx-click="banner_position"
                phx-value-pos="banner-example-1"
                variant="outline"
                color="warning"
              >
                Show natural
              </.button>
              <.button
                color="misc"
                variant="outline"
                size="small"
                phx-click="banner_position"
                phx-value-pos="banner-example-110"
              >
                Show White
              </.button>
              <.button
                color="natural"
                variant="outline"
                size="small"
                phx-click="banner_position"
                phx-value-pos="banner-example-111"
              >
                Show Dark
              </.button>
              <.button
                color="info"
                variant="outline"
                size="small"
                phx-click="banner_position"
                phx-value-pos="banner-example-3"
              >
                Show Info
              </.button>
              <.button
                color="success"
                variant="outline"
                size="small"
                phx-click="banner_position"
                phx-value-pos="banner-example-4"
              >
                Show Success
              </.button>
              <.button
                color="warning"
                variant="outline"
                size="small"
                phx-click="banner_position"
                phx-value-pos="banner-example-5"
              >
                Show Warning
              </.button>
              <.button
                color="danger"
                variant="outline"
                size="small"
                phx-click="banner_position"
                phx-value-pos="banner-example-6"
              >
                Show Danger
              </.button>
              <.button
                color="silver"
                variant="outline"
                size="small"
                phx-click="banner_position"
                phx-value-pos="banner-example-7"
              >
                Show silver
              </.button>
              <.button
                color="misc"
                variant="outline"
                size="small"
                phx-click="banner_position"
                phx-value-pos="banner-example-8"
              >
                Show Misc
              </.button>
              <.button
                color="dawn"
                variant="outline"
                size="small"
                phx-click="banner_position"
                phx-value-pos="banner-example-9"
              >
                Show Dawn
              </.button>
              <.button
                color="primary"
                variant="outline"
                size="small"
                phx-click="banner_position"
                phx-value-pos="banner-example-10"
              >
                Show Primary
