          <.cp>
            The shadow variant of the Mishka Chelekom banner is similar to the default variant, but it also includes a subtle shadow along with a border and natural background in silver mode.
          </.cp>

          <.custom_code_wrapper code_class="text-sm" code={@code_3}>
