              Bordered Variant
            </.link>
          </.heading2>

          <.cp>
            The Bordered variant of the Mishka Chelekom banner has lighter background and a border. Bordered variant have also white and dark colors which are the same colors in the dark and light mode.
          </.cp>

          <.custom_code_wrapper code_class="text-sm" code={@code_15}>
            <div class="mb-6 flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
