          <.heading2 margin="my-5" id="border-prop-banner">
            <.link patch={~p"/chelekom/docs/banner/#border-prop-banner"}>
              Border prop in Phoenix LiveView banner component
            </.link>
          </.heading2>

          <.cp>
            The border prop offers values like <.custom_inline_code>extra_small</.custom_inline_code>, <.custom_inline_code>small</.custom_inline_code>, <.custom_inline_code>medium</.custom_inline_code>, <.custom_inline_code>large</.custom_inline_code>, and <.custom_inline_code>extra_large</.custom_inline_code>. These values control the border size of the banner, allowing you to adjust the thickness to suit your design. Additionally, you can use boolean props such as <.custom_inline_code>left_border</.custom_inline_code>, <.custom_inline_code>right_border</.custom_inline_code>, <.custom_inline_code>hide_border</.custom_inline_code>, and
            <.custom_inline_code>full_border</.custom_inline_code>
            to change the border position, add, or remove borders as needed for greater customization.
          </.cp>

          <.custom_code_wrapper code_class="text-sm" code={@code_6}>
            <div class="mb-6 flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
              <.button
                size="small"
                phx-click="banner_position"
                phx-value-pos="banner-example-56"
                variant="outline"
                color="info"
              >
                Show Extra Small Border
              </.button>
              <.button
                color="success"
                variant="outline"
                size="small"
                phx-click="banner_position"
                phx-value-pos="banner-example-57"
              >
                Show Small Border
              </.button>
              <.button
                color="warning"
                variant="outline"
                size="small"
                phx-click="banner_position"
                phx-value-pos="banner-example-58"
              >
                Show Medium Border
              </.button>
              <.button
                color="danger"
                variant="outline"
                size="small"
                phx-click="banner_position"
                phx-value-pos="banner-example-59"
              >
                Show Large Border
